#: doc/guix.texi:12378
msgid ""
"This is the type of services that run @var{dhcp}, a Dynamic Host "
"Configuration Protocol (DHCP) client, on all the non-loopback network "
"interfaces.  Its value is the DHCP client package to use, @code{isc-dhcp} by "
"default."
